sentences: Ole Brask (April 4, 1935 – March 23, 2009) was a Danish photographer who specialized in jazz photography.
There are two published collections of his work; Jazz People published in 1976 by H. N. Abrams, New York City and Ole Brask Photographs Jazz published in 1995 by Nieswand Verlag Germany.
